        <abstract>
            <p>Is assembling apparatus of lenses and reflector to observe flower from opening to first shedding of pollen, and to determine whether fertilisation is by night- or day-feeders.</p> 
<p>Will also examine reasons for absence of nectar in <hi rend="italic">Polygala linaria</hi>.</p> 
        </abstract>
